<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石<delay20 />是石头吗～？<delay frames="40" />
还是骨头呢～？<delay frames="40" />
唔～<delay20 />到底是哪个呢<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像具体是哪个都无所谓呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要知道它很帅就好了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这些化石，<delay20 />都是3亿年前<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真实生活在地球上的生物吧～？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />3亿年～<delay20 />
是我<delay8 />出生前多久呢～？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要怎么样<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />才能成为化石呢～？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />是不是只要多摄入一些钙<delay20 />
来强化骨质就可以了呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这块化石好大呀～<delay frames="40" />
到底要吃些什么<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能长到这么大呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />好大呀～！<delay frames="40" />
太帅了吧～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想要成为这样的化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我应该要多吃点，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让自己长得更大些才行～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在很久以前，地球上生活着<delay8 />
那么多体型庞大的生物，<delay20 />
这也就是说，那时候食物应该非常充沛吧～<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻～<delay20 />
我有点<delay8 />羡慕了呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会不会有一天突然动起来呢～？<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我忍不住会常来看一看～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我前段时间<delay20 />做了个梦，<delay8 />
梦见这里的化石动起来了～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />动作僵硬，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看上去却很开心呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">化石<delay8 />究竟是谁制作出来的呢～？<delay frames="40" />
如果能有幸认识这个人，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我一定去求对方，<delay frames="40" />
就说<delay8 /><anim id="Apologize" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把我也变成化石～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里有你想要看的化石吗～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有别的房间里也有化石，<delay20 />
你可以慢慢欣赏哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />你住的<tag a="110" b="32" />上的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
是什么样子的呢～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有机会给我详细描述一下吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要变成化石，<delay20 />
首先要对化石知根知底才行～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以，<delay20 />我现在是来学习的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听说大家翘首以盼的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />
终于建成了，<delay20 />
于是就过来探险啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这么多化石<delay8 />陈列在这里，<delay8 />
真的好震撼啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay8 />真厉害～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />好棒啊～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鱼、虫子、<delay8 />化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里有好多可以展示的呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等展品数量再多一些，<delay20 />
这里一定会成为<tag a="110" b="33" />的<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />著名景点的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听说<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="32" />上建成了一座很棒的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
所以<delay8 />特意过来看看～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里的层高很高～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是<delay8 />巨大的恐龙化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也可以很轻松地
放进来展示～</message>
</msbt>